element.text: Tap the screen to pop up the heart

attributes.information: Deoxygenated blood is pumped from the body through the Vena Cava to the right atrium.
attributes.title: Right Atrium

attributes.information: The right ventricle receives the deoxygenated blood from the right atrium and pumps the blood to the lungs for oxygenation.
attributes.title: Right Ventricle

attributes.information: Oxygenated blood is pumped from the lungs through the pulmonary vein to the left atrium.
attributes.title: Left Atrium

attributes.information: The left ventricle receives oxygenated blood from the left atrium and pumps the blood out to the body for circulation.
attributes.title: Left Ventricle

element.text: Receives non-oxygenated blood from the body's largest veins (Vena Cava).
Point at the AR marker and tap Get Started to begin the experience.
